      "parameters": {
        "width": 624,
        "height": 608,
        "content": "## Automated Review Monitoring with Decodo, Google Sheets, Gemini AI & Telegram Alerts\n\nGreat For:\n• E-commerce owners\n• Product managers\n• Reputation & CX teams\n• Amazon/Marketplace sellers\n• Anyone who wants hands-off, scheduled review monitoring + alerts\n\nWhat It Does:\n- Reads URLs from Google Sheets\n- Loops through each product URL\n- Scrapes reviews using Decodo\n- Converts scraped data into clean text\n- Detects sentiment (positive / neutral / negative)\n- Summarizes all reviews\n- Sends Telegram alerts when needed\n- Stores all results in a review log sheet\n\nWhy It’s Useful:\n- Fully automated review monitoring\n- Daily digest + alerts for negative sentiment\n- Structured historical record of reviews\n- Works without coding\n- Upgradable (translation, classification, etc.)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
